      "parameters": {
        "content": "Workflow purpose:\nSend a simple daily Gmail notification with the EduTech Letter site URL and attach the headline card image.\n\nAfter import:\n1. Open the Gmail node.\n2. Connect your Gmail credential.\n3. Set the To field to your email address.\n4. Optionally add CC/BCC recipients in the Gmail node.\n5. Activate the workflow.",
